I wanted to send a quick thank you to all of you.
Everything about the process has been amazing. From Esther’s help with the initial meetings to Tim helping me with the offboarding with our previous company and finally with Ahmad coming down and helping us out, everything was amazing.
I am so grateful for your team.
Everyone has been very kind and helpful with everything.
We have already had one of our employees call for assistance and mentioned to me that they were impressed with the help they received.

originalText.text: I have worked with three reps from RCS and each were professional, courteous, knowledgeable and kind.  They helped me get port from one computer to another, fix some glitches and add email accounts to my own accounts.  I recommend Nick E and Ralph and would be happy to work with them again!
